{"tid":1711524,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「幫推」 香港人突破樽頸方法","createTime":"2019-11-12T11:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T13:13:58.000Z","uid":3209,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"911aecfa700c68697b213a97725656b146f9f82f","tid":1711524,"uid":3209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"方法就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">千其唔好</span>[size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\">]一方有難 八方支援！</span>[/size=6<br />\n中大割地 讀過書既連登諗起咩阿<br />\n六國之弊 弊左賂秦阿<br />\n清政府北洋艦隊俾日軍全滅<br />\n除左佢地硬實力廢因為咩阿<br />\n因為南洋艦隊 福建艦隊食花生阿嘛<br />\n點解今日中環 由12點玩到3:30 先放TG<br />\n但IFC / 愛丁堡 / 交易廣場 / 港交所 12點就駐曬POPO?<br />\n因為佢驚中環集會現場係煙幕 一開打你地班暴徒就搞其他地方阿<br />\n中大手足 打生打死<br />\n打到成隊新界南過曬去<br />\n如果以後<br />\n中大一開大片/其他地方開大片<br />\n你地班暴徒<span style=\"color: red;\">千其唔好</span>立即係附近幾區一齊開花<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千其唔好</span></span>咁快 咁即興<br />\n咁中大班暴徒同主戰場就有休息機會喇<br />\n我地偉大既香港警隊仲點止暴制亂阿<br />\n<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千其唔好</span></span>一開大片 附近區一齊call馬快閃開花<br />\n<br />\n以後個模式<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千其唔好</span></span> 圍魏救趙<br />\n一方受襲 八方支援<br />\n香港暴徒<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">千其唔好</span>進化"},{"pid":"4a5503bdb638e1dbd4a78131aa36561aa4fcb83b","tid":1711524,"uid":3209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:52:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79105a74b22a55efff51fa05ae3b59a1d4278c8e","tid":1711524,"uid":3209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"03e5ec44d620e4ec924b74d33bfb71629d274359","tid":1711524,"uid":3209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"c2f56db1d483db7e97d94419345dce99b900c66a","tid":1711524,"uid":3209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:53:37.000Z","msg":"甴你老尾"},{"pid":"a5e52edb0ada8e2dcee7e1eebd2032